1. get player_name
2. get buy_in
  a. check money input
  b. check valid buy in
  c. set buy in
3. get bet
  a. check money input
  b. check valid bet
  c. set bet
4. game proper
  a. shuffle deck (optional)
  b. deal cards
  c. dealer check hole
  d. player move
  e. dealer move
  f. find winner
5. check if play again or start over
